《'''L.U.C.A.: The Beginning'''》（{{韓|諺=루카: 더 비기닝}}），為[[大韓民國|韓國]][[tvN|tvN]]於2021年2月1日起播出的[[tvN月火連續劇|月火連續劇]]，由《[[Voice_(韓國電視劇)|Voice]]》導演[[金洪善|金洪善]]和《[[致親愛的法官大人|致親愛的法官大人]]》編劇[[千成日|千成日]]合作打造。此劇講述因特殊能力而被追逐的池伍（[[金來沅|金來沅]]飾）與唯一記得他模樣的重案組刑警天具雲（[[李多熙_(演員)|李多熙]]飾）一同對抗世界的故事。<ref>{{cite web|author=Rui|url=https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/123826|title=李多熙擔任新劇《Luca》女主角，不穿時裝穿警服|publisher=韓星網|date=2020-01-29|language=zh-hant|accessdate=2021-01-12|archive-date=2021-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113213818/https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/123826|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=MiJimin|url=https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/125905|title=全新「長腿CP」組合！金來沅&李多熙確定合作tvN科幻新劇《LUCA》已開拍！|publisher=韓星網|date=2020-04-14|language=zh-hant|accessdate=2021-01-12|archive-date=2021-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113200505/https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/125905|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=MiJimin|url=https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/130483|title=「長腿CP」金來沅&李多熙主演 tvN 新劇《LUCA》完成拍攝，歷代級CG引人期待！|publisher=韓星網|date=2020-09-29|language=zh-hant|accessdate=2021-01-12|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115035049/https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/130483|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=草莓|url=https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/132707|title=超越極限、華麗的追擊動作劇！金來沅、李多熙新戲《LUCA》2/1首播|publisher=韓星網|date=2021-01-01|language=zh-hant|accessdate=2021-01-12|archive-date=2021-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114230535/https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/132707|dead-url=no}}</ref>

